<i>Tae-seo.</i>

237
00:24:28,175 --> 00:24:32,304
<i>Tren 4654, boleh bergerak sekarang.</i>

238
00:24:33,722 --> 00:24:37,142
<i>Pintu sedang ditutup.</i>

239
00:24:57,621 --> 00:24:59,706
Pintu ditutup. Pintu skrin ditutup.

240
00:25:00,498 --> 00:25:01,625
Tren bergerak.

241
00:25:23,188 --> 00:25:28,735
<i>Sila awasi langkah anda.</i>

242
00:25:46,920 --> 00:25:49,256
TREN TERAKHIR KE OIDO
TREN TERAKHIR KE ANSAN

243
00:25:57,806 --> 00:25:59,766
UNIT 610

244
00:26:03,061 --> 00:26:05,605
Dalam perjalanan. Saya di Stesen Isu.

245
00:26:05,689 --> 00:26:09,276
<i>Si Seong-chan tiba-tiba telefon saya.</i>

246
00:26:09,359 --> 00:26:12,028
<i>Lepas saya beritahu</i>
<i>awak datang ke rumah saya hari ini,</i>

247
00:26:12,112 --> 00:26:14,197
habislah kalau dia datang.

248
00:26:16,116 --> 00:26:19,494
Na-yeong fikir kita kenal
melalui Seong-chan.

249
00:26:19,577 --> 00:26:22,831
<i>Saya cakap awak akan telefon saya</i>
<i>apabila sampai di Stesen Isu,</i>

250
00:26:22,914 --> 00:26:24,207
<i>kita jumpa di sana.</i>

251
00:26:24,291 --> 00:26:25,417
<i>Saya asyik bercakap.</i>

252
00:26:26,293 --> 00:26:28,169
<i>Dia takkan tunggu awak di sana, bukan?</i>

253
00:26:31,172 --> 00:26:32,799
Nanti saya telefon semula.

254
00:26:39,973 --> 00:26:41,558
Awak buat apa di sini?

255
00:26:43,351 --> 00:26:44,436
Eun-a.

256
00:26:51,484 --> 00:26:52,652
Mari kita ke Tongyeong.

257
00:26:52,736 --> 00:26:53,778
Tak nak.

258
00:26:54,779 --> 00:26:55,905
Saya perlu masa.

259
00:26:55,989 --> 00:26:59,367
Awak hilang selepas kata
nak pergi tutup rumah tamu.

260
00:27:03,163 --> 00:27:04,831
<i>Pintu sedang ditutup.</i>

261
00:27:26,519 --> 00:27:28,396
Awak pun kena tahu!

262
00:27:54,005 --> 00:27:55,256
Eun-a!

263
00:28:16,611 --> 00:28:17,612
Eun-a.

264
00:28:18,279 --> 00:28:19,656
Eun-a.

265
00:28:41,761 --> 00:28:43,054
Yeon Tae-seo.

266
00:29:12,000 --> 00:29:13,501
SEONG-CHAN

267
00:29:35,940 --> 00:29:38,193
Dah 10 tahun kita jadi rakan sekerja.

268
00:29:38,276 --> 00:29:40,236
Kita bukan bercinta, kenapa perlu masa?

269
00:29:41,112 --> 00:29:44,157
Barulah awak tak cari
dan sampaikan berita buruk.

270
00:29:44,240 --> 00:29:46,868
Kita pasangan kerja,
kita kena kongsi tanggungjawab.

271
00:29:47,452 --> 00:29:49,287
Ya, kami rakan kerja. Puas hati?

272
00:29:50,371 --> 00:29:51,873
Itu cara mereka.

273
00:29:51,956 --> 00:29:54,667
Kalau untung, mereka singkir
yang urus dan ambil alih.

274
00:29:54,751 --> 00:29:56,878
Kita diperdaya pihak jahat.

275
00:29:56,961 --> 00:29:58,963
Bukan salah awak. Kalau kita menang saman…

276
00:29:59,047 --> 00:30:00,215
Kita dapat apa?

277
00:30:00,298 --> 00:30:01,716
Kita tak boleh biar mereka…

278
00:30:04,886 --> 00:30:06,888
Tak boleh biar mereka berniaga juga.

279
00:30:06,971 --> 00:30:09,474
Kalau saman lama, mereka rugi juga.

280
00:30:09,557 --> 00:30:10,934
Saya akan teruskan.

281
00:30:12,894 --> 00:30:14,354
Saya tak nak tahu.

282
00:30:15,188 --> 00:30:16,815
Saya tak nak dengar.

283
00:30:25,824 --> 00:30:27,200
Awak dah sejauh ini.

284
00:30:28,368 --> 00:30:29,577
Kenapa Seoul?

285
00:30:33,414 --> 00:30:35,166
Saya akan selalu datang.

286
00:30:35,250 --> 00:30:38,711
Jangan. Saya benci ulang-alik,
selaraskan jadual.

287
00:30:41,005 --> 00:30:42,882
Kerja di sini ringkas dan mudah.

288
00:30:43,633 --> 00:30:45,260
Bagus untuk mengisi masa.

289
00:30:45,343 --> 00:30:46,511
Saya selesa.

290
00:30:52,809 --> 00:30:54,727
Awak dah lalui macam-macam.

291
00:30:55,979 --> 00:30:57,730
Hati-hati balik.

292
00:33:02,188 --> 00:33:03,398
Helo, cikgu.

293
00:33:03,481 --> 00:33:06,025
<i>Hei, kenapa kirim banyak sangat</i>
<i>duit hadiah kahwin?</i>

294
00:33:06,651 --> 00:33:07,694
Tak adalah.

295
00:33:07,777 --> 00:33:09,988
Saya patut datang.

296
00:33:10,071 --> 00:33:11,698
<i>Awak sibuk, tak payahlah.</i>

297
00:33:11,781 --> 00:33:13,908
<i>Hui-seo banyak membantu.</i>

298
00:33:13,992 --> 00:33:17,620
<i>Dia kutip semua bayaran di kaunter</i>
<i>dan agihkan kupon makan.</i>

299
00:33:17,704 --> 00:33:19,998
<i>Pelajar ramai daripada jangkaan,</i>
<i>kelam-kabut.</i>

300
00:33:20,081 --> 00:33:21,874
<i>Tapi Hui-seo urus semuanya.</i>

301
00:33:21,958 --> 00:33:24,168
Budak kelas saya datang?

302
00:33:24,252 --> 00:33:26,087
<i>Nak kata mereka rakan sekelas pun…</i>

303
00:33:26,170 --> 00:33:28,256
<i>Yang awak benar-benar kenal…</i>

304
00:33:28,339 --> 00:33:29,716
Eun-a…

305
00:33:30,425 --> 00:33:32,468
Tak ada dengar khabar dia, bukan?

306
00:33:33,219 --> 00:33:36,305
<i>Tak tahu. Tak ada sesiapa tahu.</i>

307
00:33:36,389 --> 00:33:38,349
<i>Awak pun tak berhubung dengan dia, bukan?</i>

308
00:33:39,308 --> 00:33:40,685
Ya.

309
00:33:40,768 --> 00:33:42,103
<i>Mungkin bulan lepas?</i>

310
00:33:42,186 --> 00:33:44,480
<i>Ada petisyen difailkan bawah nama Eun-a.</i>

311
00:33:45,189 --> 00:33:47,400
<i>Saya dengar ada dokumen</i>
<i>difailkan secara cuai</i>

312
00:33:48,026 --> 00:33:50,653
<i>untuk robohkan rumahnya.</i>

313
00:33:51,612 --> 00:33:53,906
<i>Isteri saya bekerja di pejabat daerah.</i>

314
00:33:54,615 --> 00:33:58,578
<i>Perobohan rumah kosong</i>
<i>perlukan banyak dokumen rumit,</i>

315
00:33:58,661 --> 00:34:02,206
<i>tapi cuma ada sekeping kertas</i>
<i>atas nama Eun-a.</i>

316
00:34:07,503 --> 00:34:08,796
Ini sampai melalui pos.

317
00:34:10,256 --> 00:34:11,841
{\an8}Ini memang tak masuk akal.

318
00:34:11,924 --> 00:34:14,802
{\an8}Perobohan rumah kosong
hasilkan bertan-tan sisa,

319
00:34:14,886 --> 00:34:16,763
jadi perlu alamat penghantaran.

320
00:34:16,846 --> 00:34:18,056
Mereka tulis rumah Eun-a.

321
00:34:18,765 --> 00:34:22,351
Jadi selepas dirobohkan,
sisa itu nak ditimbun di situ?

322
00:34:23,478 --> 00:34:25,563
Tiada nombor telefon, saya buntu.

323
00:34:29,233 --> 00:34:30,068
Yeon Tae-seo!

324
00:34:30,151 --> 00:34:31,402
Apa ini?

325
00:34:32,070 --> 00:34:32,904
Itu abang saya.

326
00:34:32,987 --> 00:34:34,322
{\an8}- Begitu.
- Abang!

327
00:34:34,405 --> 00:34:36,657
{\an8}- Dia kebanggaan Yeonwoo.
- Begitu.

328
00:34:36,741 --> 00:34:38,076
Kenapa abang datang?

329
00:34:38,159 --> 00:34:39,368
Abang patut beritahu.

330
00:34:39,452 --> 00:34:41,120
Dialah yang saya selalu sebut.

331
00:34:41,204 --> 00:34:43,748
- Rakan sekerja di pejabat pos.
- Helo.

332
00:34:43,831 --> 00:34:46,751
- Ini mentor saya.
- Hui-seo selalu cerita.

333
00:34:50,963 --> 00:34:52,215
{\an8}Kenapa balik?

334
00:34:54,759 --> 00:34:56,886
Tiga tahun lepas
tiba-tiba balik hari minggu

335
00:34:57,678 --> 00:35:00,515
sampaikan berita tergempar
berhenti kerja syarikat besar.

336
00:35:01,265 --> 00:35:02,600
Aduh, saya masih trauma.

337
00:35:02,683 --> 00:35:05,520
Abang balik membebel,
tak balik pun membebel.

338
00:35:05,603 --> 00:35:06,562
Kerja okey?

339
00:35:06,646 --> 00:35:08,773
Pejabat pos lumpuh tanpa saya.

340
00:35:08,856 --> 00:35:10,691
Bukankah saya dah beritahu?

341
00:35:11,359 --> 00:35:13,361
Jangan risau tentang saya.

342
00:35:14,737 --> 00:35:15,988
Betul.

343
00:35:17,073 --> 00:35:20,118
Sepanjang hidup,
abang begitu bertanggungjawab.

344
00:35:20,201 --> 00:35:22,286
Kenapa sekarang abang buat hal?

345
00:35:22,370 --> 00:35:26,457
Saya tak pernah fikir saya akan
risaukan abang apabila saya dewasa.

346
00:35:32,255 --> 00:35:34,966
Hei. Makan dulu, okey?

347
00:35:35,049 --> 00:35:37,718
Nenek tak masak banyak
sebab kamu tak beritahu.

348
00:35:38,469 --> 00:35:41,347
Biar saya buat alang-alang saya balik.
Ada apa-apa lagi?

349
00:35:41,430 --> 00:35:43,224
Tak ada. Mari makan.

350
00:35:46,602 --> 00:35:47,937
Letak di sini.

351
00:35:48,020 --> 00:35:49,438
Lambatnya datuk.

352
00:35:50,273 --> 00:35:53,359
Dulu dia rajin bekerja di ladang orang.

353
00:35:53,442 --> 00:35:56,445
Sekarang ada ladang sendiri,
dia ibarat tinggal di sana.

354
00:35:56,529 --> 00:35:58,531
Bagus ada ladang sendiri.

355
00:35:59,991 --> 00:36:02,660
Usia begini hidup selesa
hasil usaha cucu-cucu.

356
00:36:03,744 --> 00:36:06,956
Aduhai, nenek terlupa <i>kimchi.</i>
Biar nenek ambil.

357
00:36:07,039 --> 00:36:10,001
- Saya nak pergi simpan ini di stor dulu.
- Okey.

358
00:36:41,574 --> 00:36:46,537
{\an8}PASAR MINI

359
00:37:14,190 --> 00:37:16,359
Ya? Ada apa?

360
00:37:18,027 --> 00:37:19,737
Siapa ini?

361
00:37:20,488 --> 00:37:21,489
Nenek apa khabar?

362
00:37:23,157 --> 00:37:24,575
Eun-a ada datang, bukan?

363
00:37:25,159 --> 00:37:27,328
Lukisan sayur itu dia punya.

364
00:37:28,079 --> 00:37:29,080
Dia tak datang.

365
00:37:30,122 --> 00:37:31,499
Maaf.

366
00:37:44,095 --> 00:37:45,137
Tolong berikan.

367
00:37:45,221 --> 00:37:46,639
{\an8}010-0922-1109
YEON TAE-SEO

368
00:37:46,722 --> 00:37:48,975
{\an8}Saya terserempak dengan dia di Seoul.

369
00:37:52,478 --> 00:37:55,106
Eun-a baik-baik di Seoul?

370
00:37:56,357 --> 00:37:58,234
Saya rasa tak.

371
00:37:59,819 --> 00:38:00,903
Kebetulan ternampak.

372
00:38:01,946 --> 00:38:04,824
Taklah. Dia baik-baik saja.

373
00:38:10,121 --> 00:38:11,580
Ini dia.

374
00:38:11,664 --> 00:38:14,834
Dia hantar kad Krismas setiap hari.

375
00:38:14,917 --> 00:38:20,256
Ini dihantar daripada hotel dan asrama.
Itu tempat dia bekerja dulu.

376
00:38:21,173 --> 00:38:22,174
Yang ini.

377
00:38:23,968 --> 00:38:25,261
Ini tahun lepas.

378
00:38:34,312 --> 00:38:36,314
<i>Nenek, apa khabar?</i>

379
00:38:37,064 --> 00:38:40,151
<i>Saya rasa saya akan tinggal di sini.</i>

380
00:38:41,610 --> 00:38:42,903
Dia baik-baik saja.

381
00:38:52,955 --> 00:38:54,040
<i>Berhenti.</i>

382
00:38:55,124 --> 00:38:56,167
<i>Tak perlulah…</i>

383
00:38:57,335 --> 00:38:58,836
<i>risau dan runsing.</i>

384
00:39:00,171 --> 00:39:01,172
<i>Sudah.</i>

385
00:39:23,861 --> 00:39:26,364
<i>Saya sertakan foto</i>
<i>kerana boleh didedahkan.</i>

386
00:39:26,447 --> 00:39:27,823
<i>Saiz 13 kali 18 sentimeter.</i>

387
00:39:27,907 --> 00:39:31,160
<i>Tanpa kaca.</i>
<i>Paling kurang 10 sentimeter ruang tepi.</i>

388
00:39:32,078 --> 00:39:35,873
<i>Boleh cari dalam talian</i>
<i>Warisan Budaya Rakyat: Rumah Lama.</i>

389
00:39:39,293 --> 00:39:41,003
AKANKU CARI JIKA DUNIA TAK MAHU

390
00:39:41,087 --> 00:39:41,921
<i>Susunannya</i>

391
00:39:42,713 --> 00:39:46,175
oak, ceri, walnut, dan mapel.

392
00:39:47,051 --> 00:39:48,177
Tengok macam mana.

393
00:39:51,472 --> 00:39:53,349
Boleh biar ruang tepi macam ini

394
00:39:53,974 --> 00:39:56,227
atau rapatkan bingkai.

395
00:40:01,023 --> 00:40:02,024
Yang ini.

396
00:40:03,442 --> 00:40:05,986
Biarkan ruang tepi bagus juga.

397
00:40:06,070 --> 00:40:07,530
Boleh guna kertas tradisional?

398
00:40:07,613 --> 00:40:08,989
Boleh.

399
00:40:11,075 --> 00:40:12,284
Apa kerja harian awak?

400
00:40:16,622 --> 00:40:17,790
Pengendali tren.

401
00:40:18,916 --> 00:40:20,376
Begitu.

402
00:40:20,459 --> 00:40:21,836
Tak bekerja hari ini?

403
00:40:21,919 --> 00:40:24,046
Saya kerja esok petang. Syif malam.

404
00:40:24,839 --> 00:40:26,715
Lima semuanya. Nama awak?

405
00:40:28,175 --> 00:40:30,302
Im A-sol.

406
00:40:30,386 --> 00:40:31,929
Cik Im A-sol.

407
00:40:33,264 --> 00:40:34,807
Jenis kayu, oak.

408
00:40:35,641 --> 00:40:36,976
Minggu ketiga

409
00:40:38,477 --> 00:40:40,104
bulan depan. Betul?

410
00:40:41,021 --> 00:40:42,857
Apa yang seronok jadi pengendali tren?

411
00:40:44,275 --> 00:40:45,401
Seronok…

412
00:40:46,777 --> 00:40:50,030
Seronok sebab tak bawa kerja balik rumah.

413
00:40:51,073 --> 00:40:52,533
Bagusnya.

414
00:40:52,616 --> 00:40:53,951
Saya pun ada soalan.

415
00:40:54,660 --> 00:40:56,912
Kenapa pilih saya untuk kerja ini?

416
00:40:57,496 --> 00:41:00,040
Saya tak pernah buat
untuk selain rakan sekerja.

417
00:41:00,958 --> 00:41:02,501
Saya nampak di restoran.

418
00:41:03,252 --> 00:41:07,840
Foto pemandangan ada bingkai
setaraf galeri seni, jadi saya tanya.

419
00:41:07,923 --> 00:41:10,384
Saya semak akaun media sosial di belakang.

420
00:41:11,260 --> 00:41:14,346
Boleh saya upah awak untuk bingkai lain?

421
00:41:14,430 --> 00:41:16,599
Tiada tarikh akhir. Untuk lukisan minyak.

422
00:41:17,933 --> 00:41:19,018
Saiznya berapa?

423
00:41:19,101 --> 00:41:20,978
Kira-kira…

424
00:41:21,061 --> 00:41:22,313
Sebesar ini?

425
00:41:22,396 --> 00:41:25,024
Atau sebesar ini?

426
00:41:29,028 --> 00:41:30,404
Tunggu lima minit.

427
00:41:33,532 --> 00:41:34,575
Apa?

428
00:41:46,420 --> 00:41:47,338
Apa benda?

429
00:41:55,179 --> 00:41:57,598
- Ini dia.
- Awak tinggal berhampiran?

430
00:41:57,681 --> 00:41:59,767
- Ya.
- Saya…

431
00:41:59,850 --> 00:42:03,437
Ini lukisan pertama saya beli.

432
00:42:03,521 --> 00:42:05,981
Jatuh ke lantai apabila tali putus,

433
00:42:07,358 --> 00:42:09,318
bingkai hancur.

434
00:42:09,401 --> 00:42:12,947
Saya tak pernah buat untuk lukisan
sebelum ini. Memang besar.

435
00:42:13,030 --> 00:42:15,074
Bagus. Saya nak bingkai baru sepenuhnya.

436
00:42:16,408 --> 00:42:18,035
Kira-kira saiznya?

437
00:42:19,370 --> 00:42:20,829
Saya tak ada pita ukur.

438
00:42:22,164 --> 00:42:23,832
Tak apa.

439
00:42:23,916 --> 00:42:26,418
Awak boleh ukur di rumah,
hantar pada saya.

440
00:42:26,502 --> 00:42:27,670
Okey.

441
00:42:29,213 --> 00:42:30,965
Biar saya ambil gambar dulu.

442
00:42:31,632 --> 00:42:32,716
Boleh ambil gambar?

443
00:42:44,061 --> 00:42:47,189
Pemilik restoran kata pembuat bingkai dulu
seorang pengaturcara.

444
00:42:47,273 --> 00:42:49,108
Awaklah orangnya, bukan?

445
00:42:49,191 --> 00:42:50,776
Restoran mana?

446
00:42:50,859 --> 00:42:53,445
Di bawah pusat belajar.

447
00:42:53,529 --> 00:42:55,364
Pusat belajar Hyeong-seok.

448
00:42:56,156 --> 00:42:57,866
Kalau itu, betullah saya.

449
00:42:57,950 --> 00:43:01,245
Dulu awak pengatur cara.
Begitu rupa-rupanya.

450
00:43:01,328 --> 00:43:02,871
Kenapa? Ada apa-apa berlaku?

451
00:43:05,207 --> 00:43:06,875
Bagi saya pula,

452
00:43:06,959 --> 00:43:08,460
perkara berlaku di rumah

453
00:43:08,544 --> 00:43:10,337
dan bingkai yang elok 10 tahun

454
00:43:10,421 --> 00:43:12,256
jatuh apabila tali putus.

455
00:43:12,339 --> 00:43:13,465
Pelik, bukan?

456
00:43:15,259 --> 00:43:18,220
Saya rasa soalan macam ini
mengelirukan sebab kita baru kenal.

457
00:43:19,179 --> 00:43:21,015
Tak apa.

458
00:43:21,098 --> 00:43:23,475
Saya selalu ditanya, jadi tak kisah.

459
00:43:24,476 --> 00:43:26,437
Saya faham. Selalu ditanya.

460
00:43:27,271 --> 00:43:28,355
Hari itu…

461
00:43:29,440 --> 00:43:31,650
pelik juga bagi saya.

462
00:43:32,693 --> 00:43:36,405
Seolah-olah detik lalu bergabung dan…

463
00:43:37,906 --> 00:43:39,950
Saya bukan pandai cakap.

464
00:43:41,535 --> 00:43:44,079
Tapi memang ada hari macam itu.

465
00:43:55,341 --> 00:43:57,259
Awak pasti tak perlukan bantuan?

466
00:43:58,010 --> 00:43:58,927
Saya pasti.

467
00:44:28,832 --> 00:44:33,545
PEMBUKAAN SEMULA SELEPAS UBAH SUAI
KAFE BELAJAR MAEUM

468
00:44:39,510 --> 00:44:41,637
Nampak tak ini kafe belajar sekarang?

469
00:44:41,720 --> 00:44:43,138
Ya, nampak.

470
00:44:43,639 --> 00:44:47,267
Ruang nampak cerah
selepas semua tingkap dibuka.

471
00:44:47,351 --> 00:44:50,270
Dulu, gelap bantu fokus.

472
00:44:50,354 --> 00:44:51,522
Sekarang terbalik.

473
00:44:51,605 --> 00:44:54,400
Mereka lebih fokus
apabila orang lalu-lalang.

474
00:44:54,483 --> 00:44:56,485
Puan, saya datang.

475
00:44:56,568 --> 00:44:58,612
- Ya.
- Dua khinzir goreng pedas.

476
00:44:59,613 --> 00:45:00,739
Yang itu.

477
00:45:01,615 --> 00:45:02,908
Itu awak yang buat.

478
00:45:02,991 --> 00:45:05,786
Jadi awak yang beritahu pemilik
tentang kerja lama saya.

479
00:45:05,869 --> 00:45:07,830
Apa awak tiba-tiba cakap ini?

480
00:45:10,165 --> 00:45:11,500
Nak minum?

481
00:45:11,583 --> 00:45:13,085
Jarang berlaku.

482
00:45:13,168 --> 00:45:14,378
Ada panggilan masuk.

483
00:45:25,681 --> 00:45:26,807
Bukan.

484
00:45:29,810 --> 00:45:33,230
- Nombor tak dikenali.
- Kenapa awak jawab?

485
00:45:33,313 --> 00:45:36,191
- Puan, nak telur gulung juga!
- Okey.

486
00:45:50,747 --> 00:45:52,249
Dah 10 tahun saya lupa.

487
00:45:53,542 --> 00:45:54,793
Hilang.

488
00:45:55,377 --> 00:45:57,921
Tapi kerisauan lama boleh kembali?

489
00:45:58,005 --> 00:46:00,716
Kalau 10 tahun,
maksudnya lepas awak masuk universiti.

490
00:46:01,633 --> 00:46:03,552
Jadi, mungkin bukan pasal keluarga.

491
00:46:03,635 --> 00:46:06,305
Awak tak cerita hal
yang betul-betul risaukan awak.

492
00:46:07,681 --> 00:46:11,059
Sebelum masuk tentera,
awak memang lalui waktu sukar.

493
00:46:11,894 --> 00:46:13,604
Pasti pasal seorang perempuan,

494
00:46:13,687 --> 00:46:17,357
tapi awak tak nak cakap
sebab kata akan ingat balik.

495
00:46:17,441 --> 00:46:19,693
Kata awak akan mati kalau sebut kuat-kuat.

496
00:46:19,776 --> 00:46:23,280
Jadi kalau awak cerita,
bukan masalah besar.

497
00:46:23,363 --> 00:46:25,240
Masalah sebenar, awak tak pernah sebut.

498
00:46:25,324 --> 00:46:26,909
Takut ia merisaukan awak.

499
00:46:29,620 --> 00:46:30,996
Betul.

500
00:46:31,079 --> 00:46:33,624
Aduh. Itulah.

501
00:46:34,458 --> 00:46:36,877
Dah 10 tahun saya jadi
pengurus pusat belajar.

502
00:46:36,960 --> 00:46:41,507
Saya di puncak semangat bagi galakan
dan beri nasihat pada budak malas belajar.

503
00:46:41,590 --> 00:46:43,383
"Awak penting. Awak tentukan."

504
00:46:43,467 --> 00:46:46,720
"Lelaki itu hidup ikut cara dia sendiri."

505
00:46:46,803 --> 00:46:48,931
"Dia tak kuat minum, tapi apabila minum,

506
00:46:49,014 --> 00:46:51,600
fikirannya hanya pasal apa nak buat
dan arah hidupnya."

507
00:46:51,683 --> 00:46:54,061
"Awak pun kena fokus pada itu."

508
00:46:54,144 --> 00:46:56,939
"Dia masuk Universiti Kebangsaan Hanguk."

509
00:46:57,022 --> 00:47:00,025
"Dulu dia di Meja Satu."
Saya tutup dengan promosi pusat belajar.

510
00:47:01,610 --> 00:47:05,489
Jadi, jangan hidupkan semula
kerisauan lama.

511
00:47:05,572 --> 00:47:06,657
Okey?

512
00:47:06,740 --> 00:47:10,035
Awak dah lupa masa depan
yang ibu awak harapkan?

513
00:47:11,119 --> 00:47:14,122
"Yang selamat dan aman."

514
00:47:15,582 --> 00:47:17,834
Itu moto keluarga saya
apabila kahwin nanti.

515
00:47:18,669 --> 00:47:20,546
Ingat betul-betul.

516
00:47:22,673 --> 00:47:24,633
Memang aman.

517
00:47:32,516 --> 00:47:33,892
<i>"Yang selamat dan aman,</i>

518
00:47:36,019 --> 00:47:38,230
<i>tempat dia boleh cari hidup</i>
<i>tanpa susah payah."</i>

519
00:47:42,818 --> 00:47:46,947
{\an8}JANUARI 2022

520
00:47:47,030 --> 00:47:48,323
{\an8}Tae-seo.

521
00:47:48,407 --> 00:47:49,783
Ya?

522
00:47:49,866 --> 00:47:51,368
Awak akan dihantar

523
00:47:52,327 --> 00:47:54,079
ke cawangan India.

524
00:47:54,162 --> 00:47:57,249
Kita pernah bekerja dengan pasukan mereka,
ada muka dikenali.

525
00:47:58,083 --> 00:47:59,084
Itu peluang baik.

526
00:47:59,918 --> 00:48:01,378
Ya, baiklah.

527
00:48:05,173 --> 00:48:07,009
<i>Bukan apa sangat.</i>

528
00:48:07,092 --> 00:48:09,886
<i>Tapi datuk jatuh punggung</i>
<i>masa mencabut rumput.</i>

529
00:48:09,970 --> 00:48:12,431
<i>Ketua kampung kata dia pengsan.</i>

530
00:48:12,514 --> 00:48:14,016
<i>Tapi dia cuma ambil aspirin.</i>

531
00:48:14,099 --> 00:48:16,310
Dia patut… Dia patut ke hospital.

532
00:48:17,769 --> 00:48:20,689
Pastikan dia dapat ubat.
Abang singgah hujung minggu ini.

533
00:48:20,772 --> 00:48:23,108
<i>Jangan risau. Balik Tahun Baru Lunar.</i>

534
00:48:23,191 --> 00:48:25,944
<i>Orang sibuk cuma datang</i>
<i>Tahun Baru Lunar dan Chuseok.</i>

535
00:48:26,028 --> 00:48:29,656
<i>Semua berjalan lancar sebab saya.</i>
<i>Tapi tak lama.</i>

536
00:48:29,740 --> 00:48:31,241
