537
00:48:33,827 --> 00:48:35,704
<i>Saya jumpa Mak Cik Suk-hui hari ini.</i>

538
00:48:35,787 --> 00:48:38,498
<i>Dulu mak kerja dengan dia di stesen.</i>

539
00:48:38,582 --> 00:48:42,461
<i>Dia kata saya macam mak</i>
<i>apabila habis kerja dan cakap,</i>

540
