<i>- Mungkin saya mirip mak.</i>

542
00:48:47,758 --> 00:48:50,218
<i>Pagi tadi, dapat peluang kerja.</i>

543
00:48:50,302 --> 00:48:53,805
<i>Aku dengar Hui-seo cakap pasal mak</i>
<i>walaupun biasanya dia tak cerita.</i>

544
00:48:54,723 --> 00:48:58,935
<i>Petangnya pula,</i>
<i>aku lepaskan peluang pagi tadi.</i>

545
00:48:59,019 --> 00:49:00,812
<i>Abang tak nak saya periksa bilik itu?</i>

546
00:49:00,896 --> 00:49:03,357
<i>Walaupun naik bukit, harga berbaloi.</i>

547
00:49:03,440 --> 00:49:06,485
- Tak, abang nak kamu periksa.
<i>- Hentian seterusnya ialah Dongjak.</i>

548
00:49:06,568 --> 00:49:08,528
- Nanti abang telefon balik. Babai.
<i>- Pintu di sebelah…</i>

549
00:49:15,410 --> 00:49:17,704
<i>- Pintu sedang ditutup.</i>
- Hei, Hyeong-seok.

550
00:49:17,788 --> 00:49:20,374
<i>- Pintu sedang ditutup.</i>
- Tolong tengokkan bilik itu.

551
00:49:21,875 --> 00:49:24,836
Saya baru keluar tren.
Saya tak dengar tadi.

552
00:49:27,839 --> 00:49:31,218
Ada perkara berlaku pagi tadi.

553
00:49:32,219 --> 00:49:33,220
Ya.

554
00:49:34,137 --> 00:49:35,389
Okey.

555
00:49:50,362 --> 00:49:55,534
<i>Pada saat itu,</i>
<i>aku dapat rasakan dengan jelas</i>

556
00:49:55,617 --> 00:49:57,536
<i>apa yang penting bagi aku.</i>

557
00:49:57,619 --> 00:49:59,204
