<i>"Di mana?"</i>

563
00:50:16,054 --> 00:50:18,390
<i>Kalau berlaku apa-apa di rumah,</i>

564
00:50:18,473 --> 00:50:20,809
<i>jarak boleh ditempuh dalam sehari.</i>

565
00:50:23,562 --> 00:50:25,647
<i>Nanti suatu hari,</i>

566
00:50:26,690 --> 00:50:28,191
<i>aku akan buat apa aku nak.</i>

567
00:50:29,609 --> 00:50:30,777
<i>"Dengan siapa?"</i>

568
00:50:32,487 --> 00:50:33,488
<i>Diri sendiri.</i>

569
00:50:35,574 --> 00:50:37,409
<i>Satu saat bebas sekejap sebab Hui-seo.</i>

570
00:50:39,453 --> 00:50:40,620
<i>Dengan diri sendiri.</i>

571
00:50:43,790 --> 00:50:44,791
<i>Mampukah?</i>

572
00:51:18,283 --> 00:51:24,915
UNIVERSITI CHONGSHIN (ISU)

573
00:51:29,961 --> 00:51:30,921
