574
00:51:31,713 --> 00:51:35,175
<i>Setiap kali awal tahun sekolah,</i>
<i>saya fikirkan awak.</i>

575
00:51:38,678 --> 00:51:42,641
<i>Hari peringatan ibu bapa awak,</i>
<i>saya sangka awak sedih.</i>

576
00:51:45,727 --> 00:51:47,062
<i>Saya fikir,</i>

577
00:51:48,104 --> 00:51:49,564
<i>"Patutkah saya telefon?"</i>

578
00:51:50,607 --> 00:51:52,234
<i>Lepas itu, April tiba.</i>

579
00:51:53,527 --> 00:51:55,654
<i>Musim panas, saya tak jadi.</i>

580
00:51:56,530 --> 00:51:58,740
<i>Musim luruh, makin susah.</i>

581
00:52:00,492 --> 00:52:03,453
<i>Musim sejuk, saya terus lupakan.</i>

582
00:52:06,081 --> 00:52:08,041
<i>Saya ulang beberapa tahun.</i>

583
00:52:11,628 --> 00:52:13,255
<i>Tapi sekarang saya berhenti.</i>

584
00:52:15,173 --> 00:52:16,925
<i>Sebab saya dah jumpa awak.</i>

585
