607
00:55:21,067 --> 00:55:22,610
Sesuai dengan awak.

608
00:55:27,574 --> 00:55:29,826
<i>Saya telefon nak cakap jangan risau.</i>

609
00:55:29,909 --> 00:55:32,871
<i>Keadaan saya tak baik,</i>

610
00:55:32,954 --> 00:55:34,998
<i>mungkin sebab itu awak risau.</i>

611
00:55:37,876 --> 00:55:39,502
Keadaan macam mana?

612
00:55:42,005 --> 00:55:43,965
Dia nak minta maaf pada saya.

613
00:55:44,549 --> 00:55:46,342
Kami ada masalah.

614
00:55:46,426 --> 00:55:47,719
Panjang ceritanya.

615
00:55:47,802 --> 00:55:49,637
<i>Dia rakan sekerja di hotel, bukan?</i>

616
00:55:52,015 --> 00:55:53,850
Terus terang dengan dia.

617
00:55:55,852 --> 00:55:57,562
Barulah dia tak muncul tiba-tiba

618
00:55:59,439 --> 00:56:00,982
untuk minta maaf.

619
00:56:04,277 --> 00:56:07,072
<i>- Tak ada apa nak dirisaukan…</i>
- Bukan.

620
00:56:07,155 --> 00:56:08,406
Jangan risau.

621
00:56:14,162 --> 00:56:16,081
Okey, dah lewat.

622
00:56:16,164 --> 00:56:18,583
- Saya letak dulu.
